LAMMPS (2 Aug 2023 - Update 3)
package gpu 1
# Phase C LAMMPS A/B: EAM (Mishin Cu), small (4000-atom Cu FCC).

units           metal
atom_style      atomic
boundary        p p p

read_data       ../small.data
Reading data file ...
  orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (36.15 36.15 36.15)
  1 by 1 by 1 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  4000 atoms
  read_data CPU = 0.003 seconds

pair_style      eam/alloy
pair_coeff      * * ../../../tests/data/Cu_mishin1.eam.alloy Cu
Reading eam/alloy potential file ../../../tests/data/Cu_mishin1.eam.alloy with DATE: 2007-10-12

neighbor        1.0 bin
neigh_modify    every 10 delay 0 check no

velocity        all create 300.0 42 mom yes rot no

fix             1 all nve
timestep        0.001

thermo          200
thermo_style    custom step temp pe ke etotal

run             200

